      <item>
        <title>Permanently Disable Tor Auto-Start</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Patrick]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>The question is more like how to do that for any systemd service. Not<br>
specific to Tor.</p>
<p>Try this.</p>
<pre><code>sudo systemctl disable tor

sudo service tor start</code></pre>
          <p><a href="http://forums.whonix.org/t/permanently-disable-tor-auto-start/2195/4">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
